:diamond_shape_with_a_dot_inside: **Custom Vanity Roles**
Boosters will be given their own personal vanity role with a name and colour of their choice for as long as the boost persists! Speak to a member of staff to get started. __The staff team reserves the right to reject any role names which are inappropriate or in violation of our rules.__

:diamond_shape_with_a_dot_inside: **Greater Chat XP**
Our server boosters will level up faster as they chat in the server!
